    <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
    <div class="blog-detail">
        <div class="blog-detail-content">

            <h2>NovaTrust Bank <span>Current Accounts</span></h2>

            <p>NovaTrust Bank current accounts are designed to make everyday banking as simple and stress-free as possible. Whether you are managing your salary, paying bills, making online purchases or transferring money to family and friends, our current account gives you all the tools you need to stay on top of your finances with complete confidence and control.</p>

            <p>Every NovaTrust Bank current account comes with a free CheckCard that works like a check anywhere VISA is accepted. It also serves as an ATM card at any PULSE, CIRRUS or DASH affiliated Automatic Teller Machine. There are no fees for withdrawals or transactions at ATMs we operate, no charge or annual fee for using the CheckCard and no identification or checkbook required. All CheckCard purchases are clearly identified on your monthly statement so you always know exactly where your money is going.</p>

            <p>To report a lost or stolen NovaTrust Bank CheckCard or ATM Card, our support team is available Monday to Friday from 8:30am to 5:00pm. We take the security of your account extremely seriously and have advanced fraud detection systems running 24 hours a day to keep your money safe at all times.</p>

        </div>
