                        <span>What do I need to open an account?</span>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>You will need a valid government-issued photo ID such as a passport or national ID card, a proof of address dated within the last 3 months, and a valid email address and phone number.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How do I report a lost or stolen card?</span>
